name: PRVDR_SK
comment: AN IDR ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY USED TO IDENTIFY A PARTY ENGAGED IN ACTIVITY RELATED TO CMS.

name: PRVDR_HSTRY_EFCTV_DT
comment: A DATE IDENTIFYING WHEN A PROVIDER RECORD BECAME EFFECTIVE.

name: PRVDR_HSTRY_OBSLT_DT
comment: A DATE IDENTIFYING WHEN A PROVIDER RECORD BECAME OBSOLETE.

name: PRVDR_GNRC_ID_NUM
comment: A GENERIC IDENTIFIER FOR PARTIES.  FOR EXAMPLE, THIS COULD BE A UPIN, PIN, NSC SUPPLIER OR NCPDP NUMBER.

name: PRVDR_TYPE_CD
comment: IDENTIFIES THE TYPE OF LEGACY PROVIDER IDENTIFIER.

name: PRVDR_ID_QLFYR_CD
comment: THE TYPE OF DATA USED TO IDENTIFY THE SERVICE PROVIDER OF THE CLAIM:    01 = NPI  07 = NCPDP NUMBER  08 = STATE LICENSE NUMBER  11 = FEDERAL TAX NUMBER  12 = DEA

name: PRVDR_BIRTH_DT
comment: A DATE OF BIRTH OF A PROVIDER.

name: PRVDR_1ST_NAME
comment: A FIRST NAME OF A PROVIDER.

name: PRVDR_MDL_NAME
comment: A MIDDLE NAME OF A PROVIDER.

name: PRVDR_LAST_NAME
comment: A LAST NAME OF A PROVIDER.

name: PRVDR_NAME
comment: THE NAME OF THE PROVIDER.

name: PRVDR_LGL_NAME
comment: THE SELF DESIGNATED LEGAL NAME OF THE ENTITY.

name: PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: NPI NUMBER FOR MEDICAID PROVIDERS.

name: PRVDR_EMPLR_ID_NUM
comment: THE PROVIDERS EMPLOYER ID NUMBER (EMPLOYER IDENTIFICATION NUMBER  (EIN), SOCIAL SECURITY NUMBER (SSN) OR INDIVIDUAL TAX IDENTIFICATION NUMBER (ITIN))

name: PRVDR_STATE_LCNS_NUM
comment: UNIQUE NUMBER THAT IDENTIFIES A DMEPOS SUPPLIER LICENSE. (IF FROM PECOS- DMEPOS LICENSE NUMBER IN ENTITY DMEPOS LICENSE)

name: PRVDR_NCPDP_ID
comment: THE PROVIDERS NCPDP NUMBER.

name: PRVDR_UPIN_NUM
comment: A UNIQUE PROVIDER IDENTIFICATION NUMBER (UPIN) ASSIGNED TO A PROVIDER ELIGIBLE TO ORDER OR REFER SERVICES.

name: PRVDR_UPIN_GRP_NUM
comment: A UNIQUE PROVIDER IDENTIFICATION NUMBER (UPIN) ASSIGNED TO A PROVIDER ELIGIBLE TO ORDER OR REFER SERVICES.

name: PRVDR_OTHR_ID
comment: A UNIQUE HEALTHCARE PROVIDER OTHER IDENTIFICATION NUMBER.

name: PRVDR_MLG_LINE_1_ADR
comment: THE FIRST LINE OF A PARTY ADDRESS.

name: PRVDR_MLG_LINE_2_ADR
comment: THE SECOND LINE OF A PARTY ADDRESS.

name: PRVDR_INVLD_MLG_PLC_NAME
comment: INVALID MAILING PLACE NAME.  POPULATED FROM THE SOURCE WHEN INCONSISTENT WITH THE GEOGRAPHY DATA FOR THE ZIP CODE.

name: PRVDR_INVLD_MLG_ZIP_CD
comment: INVALID MAILING ZIP CODE.  POPULATED FROM THE SOURCE WHEN INCONSISTENT WITH THE GEOGRAPHY DATA FOR THE ZIP CODE.

name: PRVDR_INVLD_MLG_STATE_CD
comment: INVALID MAILING STATE CODE.  POPULATED FROM THE SOURCE WHEN INCONSISTENT WITH THE GEOGRAPHY DATA FOR THE ZIP CODE.

name: GEO_PRVDR_MLG_SK
comment: IDENTIFIER OF THE GEOGRAPHICAL AREA ASSOCIATED WITH THE PROVIDER.

name: GEO_PRVDR_MLG_ZIP4_CD
comment: A FOUR DIGIT EXTENSION TO A ZIP CODE THAT REPRESENTS A SUBDIVISION FOR MAILING PURPOSES OF THE ZIP CODE.

name: PRVDR_MLG_TEL_NUM
comment: TELEPHONE NUMBER

name: PRVDR_PRCTC_LINE_1_ADR
comment: THE FIRST LINE OF A PARTY ADDRESS.

name: PRVDR_PRCTC_LINE_2_ADR
comment: THE SECOND LINE OF A PARTY ADDRESS.

name: PRVDR_INVLD_PRCTC_PLC_NAME
comment: INVALID PRACTICE PLACE NAME.  POPULATED FROM THE SOURCE WHEN INCONSISTENT WITH THE GEOGRAPHY DATA FOR THE ZIP CODE.

name: PRVDR_INVLD_PRCTC_ZIP_CD
comment: INVALID PRACTICE ZIP CODE.  POPULATED FROM THE SOURCE WHEN INCONSISTENT WITH THE GEOGRAPHY DATA FOR THE ZIP CODE.

name: PRVDR_INVLD_PRCTC_STATE_CD
comment: INVALID PRACTICE STATE CODE.  POPULATED FROM THE SOURCE WHEN INCONSISTENT WITH THE GEOGRAPHY DATA FOR THE ZIP CODE.

name: GEO_PRVDR_PRCTC_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED NUMERIC SURROGATE KEY IDENTIFYING A PARTICULAR GEOGRAPHICAL LOCATION BY ITS FIVE-DIGIT ZIP CODE.

name: GEO_PRVDR_PRCTC_ZIP4_CD
comment: A FOUR DIGIT EXTENSION TO A ZIP CODE THAT REPRESENTS A SUBDIVISION FOR MAILING PURPOSES OF THE ZIP CODE.

name: PRVDR_PRCTC_TEL_NUM
comment: TELEPHONE NUMBER FOR THE PROVIDERÒ² PRACTICE LOCATION.

name: PRVDR_SRC_ID
comment: UNIQUE IDENTIFIER OF A SOURCE.

name: PRVDR_TXNMY_CMPST_CD
comment: A COMBINATION OF MULTIPLE NATIONAL PROVIDER PLAN ENUMERATION SYSTEM (NPPES) TAXONOMY CODES   NOTE: UP TO 15 COMBINATIONS MAY EXIST. THE DATA FROM SOURCE WILL BE STORED AS IT IS.

name: META_LST_UPDT_SK
comment: A UNIQUE LEGACY NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR), FORMULATED WITH A DATE AND 3-DIGIT SEQUENCE NUMBER, WHICH IDENTIFIES THE BATCH PROCESS THAT UPDATED A ROW IN THE IDR. DUE TO THE LIMITATION OF A 3-DIGIT VALUE, THIS IS BEING REPLACED BY META_LTST_SRC_PRCSG_ID ON NEW IDR TABLES AS THE SOURCE DATA TRACKING STANDARD.

name: META_LST_UPDT_SRC_SK
comment: A UNIQUE NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) USED TO IDENTIFY THE SPECIFIC SOURCE OF THE DATA WHEN A ROW IS UPDATED IN THE IDR.

name: META_SK
comment: A UNIQUE LEGACY NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR), FORMULATED WITH A DATE AND A 3-DIGIT SEQUENCE NUMBER, WHICH IDENTIFIES THE BATCH PROCESS THAT INITIALLY LOADED A ROW IN THE IDR. DUE TO THE LIMITATION OF A 3-DIGIT VALUE, THIS IS BEING REPLACED BY META_SRC_PRCSG_ID ON NEW IDR TABLES AS THE SOURCE DATA TRACKING STANDARD.

name: META_SRC_SK
comment: A UNIQUE NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) USED TO IDENTIFY THE SPECIFIC SOURCE OF THE DATA WHEN A ROW IS LOADED INTO THE IDR.    REFERENCE TABLE: V2_MDCR_META_DCTNRY_SRC
